<plot>Gondor is on the brink of destruction. Some think Denethor will light the beacons of the White Mountains to call for aid. However,the shadow of Mordor is spreading, encouraging the leaderless mountain goblins to come out of hiding. Their main aim is to take the beacon mountain of Halifirien (Gondor's only hope if Minas Tirith is attacked).The beacon wardens stand in the way of the goblins' domination; these wardens still hold sway over Halifirien. If Halifirien falls all hope is lost and Sauron's darkness will spread into the lands of Gondor and Rohan. The wardens will face endless hardships during an epic struggle. But,with their sacrifice will hope be once again be kindled?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?227721</url></doc>
